The paper discusses the use of machine learning for prediction and forecasting, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of a hybrid technique, which involves combining knowledge-based modeling with machine learning, which could fall under the categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with the prediction of spatiotemporal systems, which could fall under the categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
